metadata.name: Woman
metadata.description: The beginning of designing and completing and correcting the form of human figures and finding the properties and characteristics of the form of this subject was the main preoccupation of my works. By implementing this subject in small works with limited colors and gray tones, I began to study my mental issues and Over time, as the number of works grew, color was added to my work space with more variety, along with adding organic and sometimes patterned lines, and sometimes colored lines were used with the aim of activating my paintings, and finally I tried to show Giving beautiful feminine forms and a combination of sharp colors to show the identity of a woman.
